               <msContents>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <rubric>Nomina sacra; a few lines (some in groups of two) alternating with black lines on the incipit page; numbers and headings of the chapters; elements of the punctuation signs; elements of the numerals and of the quire marks.</rubric>
                     <incipit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </incipit>
                     <explicit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </explicit>
                     <note/>
                  </msItem>
                  <!--The data in the items below refers to other items. please remove this items and move the information to the appropriate place.-->
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                     <note>The Gospel chapters are wrongly numbered; 3: 22 numbered as 4; 4: 4 numbered as 5; 4: 46 numbered as 6; ch. 5 numbered as 7 etc. Cp. M. G. WECHSLER (ed.), Evangelium Iohannis Aethiopicum, Lovanii 2005 (CSCO 617 [SAe 109]).</note>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
