- Spaces for rubrication left unfilled: fols. 47v, 48r, 48v, 49r.&#xD;
- Tämälläs-sign in the shape of a cross (+) indicating the place where the reading for the day of the week ዘዘወትር, written interlineally, belongs: fol. 82va l. 6.&#xD;
- Tämälläs-sign in the shape of a cross (+) indicating the place where an omitted passage (Jn. 19: 1-2) belongs: fols. 73v-74r. &#xD;
- The name Wäldä Maryam has been written in red ink over a hardly readable noun in the supplication formula on fol. 84rb.&#xD;
- Writing exercises: fols. 1v, 3r, 85v.&#xD;
- Scribbles: fols. 3r and 85v.</item>
